        <actionDate>2010-09-15</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Passed House amended</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2010-09-24T18:30:02Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Observes the fifth anniversary of the date on which Hurricane Rita devastated the coasts of Louisiana and Texas. Expresses support to the survivors and condolences to the victims' families. </p><p> Commends the efforts of those who assisted in the response to the storm and the recovery process. </p><p>Reaffirms a commitment to rebuild, renew, and restore the Gulf Coast region.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
